		<body>
			<pb n="1"/>
				<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>New Orleans</placeName></p>
				<p rend="align(right)"><date>August 27th&#47;67</date></p>
				<p><addressee>Revd Isaac Leeser</addressee></p>
			<p rend="indent(1)"><placeName>Philadelphia</placeName></p>
			<p rend="indent(2)">Dear Sir</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">Enclosed please find<lb/> &#36;5.00 five dollars being<lb/> &#36;4.00 dollars for my yearly<lb/> subscription of the Occident.<lb/> Will you be so kind<lb/> x send me the Book<lb/> Revised by you the Title<lb/> of the Book is Prayers<lb/> x Reflections for every<lb/> occasion x situation in life<lb/> translated from the French<lb/> x adapted by <persName>Hester Rotschild</persName><lb/> please let me know<lb/> what the price of the<lb/> above book is x should<lb/> one dollar not be enough</p>
			<pb n="2"/>
				<p>I will on receipt of<lb/> same send what ever<lb/> the price is please if<lb/> it is convenient send<lb/> it <sic>imadetly</sic>  per mail&#44;<lb/> I am glad to see that<lb/> you in <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName><lb/> are going ahead.  Be<lb/> glad to hear from you<lb/> &#38; <sic>annything</sic> I can<lb/> do for you here will<lb/> be <sic>donne</sic> with pleasure<lb/> of yours Respectfully</p>
			<p rend="indent(11)"><persName role="author">S. B. Cain</persName></p>
				<p>Address</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)"><persName role="author">S. B. Cain</persName></p>
				<p>Care of <persName>J. Marks &#38; Co.</persName></p>
			<p rend="indent(1)"><placeName>98 Gravier Street</placeName></p>
			<p rend="indent(2)"><placeName>New Orleans</placeName></p>
		</body>
